数说疫情0323：国内都市恢复脉搏，欧洲确诊直逼20万，美国失业率或超“大萧条”。
Count 0323: Urban pulses are back in the country, 200,000 are diagnosed in Europe, and unemployment in the United States is high.
徐进。
Xu Jin.
