《财经》杂志官方微信。
An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
国内多地周一重现早高峰。
Early peaks returned Monday in many parts of the country.
国际奥组委确认正式考虑延期举办东京奥运会。
The International Olympic Committee has confirmed it is formally considering postponing the Games.
疫情令美国经济处在悬崖边缘。
The epidemic has brought the US economy to the brink.
意大利对中国专家组的建议照单全收。
Italy accepts the recommendations of the China Group of Experts.
文|《财经》数据研究员徐进图|《财经》视觉中心 编辑|郝洲一、国内多地重现车水马龙，湖北黄石首个解封图1今日国内简述：截至3月22日24时，国内报告新增确诊病例39例，全部为境外输入。
Photo 1: As at 2400 hours March 22, 39 new cases of confirmed illness have been reported in China, all of them imported from overseas.
湖北连续5日无新增确诊和疑似病例。
There were no new confirmed and suspected cases in Hubei for 5 consecutive days.
3月17日，中国日发电量自春节以来首次实现增长，社会生产生活加速回归常态。
On March 17, China's daily power generation increased for the first time since the Spring Festival, accelerating the return to normal social life.
今天是周一，全国多个主要大城市重现车水马龙，按百度指数北京甚至达到严重拥堵级。
Today, many major cities across the country are seeing a return to traffic, with Baidu's index of Beijing even reaching severe congestion levels.
都市脉搏正在恢复。
The urban pulse is returning.
黄石成为湖北省第一个全面解封的城市，荆门市恢复公交客运，孝感市将取消单双号管控措施。
Yellowstone became the first city in Hubei Province to be fully unsealed. Jingmen will resume bus service and Xiaogan City will abolish the control measures.
二、东京奥运会可能真的要延期了图2海外累计确诊病例已超过25万，是中国国内的三倍之多。
The number of confirmed cases overseas has reached more than 250,000, three times the number in China.
世界卫生组织紧急项目负责人瑞安（Michael Ryan）表示，各国不能够单靠封城击退疫情，否则一旦解除活动限制及封城令，疫情可能会卷土重来。
Michael Ryan, director of the World Health Organization's emergency program, said countries could not just close their cities to repel the outbreak, which could return if restrictions on movement and closures were lifted.
当务之急是要是检测及找出确诊患者及密切接触者，将他们隔离。
It is imperative to detect and identify confirmed patients and close contacts, and to isolate them.
国际奥委会（IOC）官方今天凌晨确认，正在考虑延期举办2020年东京奥运会，但不会取消。
International Olympic Committee officials confirmed early this morning that they were considering postponing the 2020 Games in Tokyo, but would not cancel them.
加拿大奥委会和澳大利亚奥委会今日相继就东京奥运会发表声明，表示希望东京奥运会推迟举办。
The Canadian Olympic Committee and the Australian Olympic Committee issued a statement today expressing hope that the Tokyo Olympic Games will be postponed.
东京奥组委内部已经在试算奥运延期的成本和花费。
TOKYO is already trying to calculate the costs and costs of the Olympics extension.
图3图4意大利果然如我们昨日所说，没有继续走湖北的线路，直接切向黄线，因此势将超越中国。
Fig. 3 Fig. 4 As we said yesterday, Italy did not continue to take Hubei route, direct to the yellow line, so it will overtake China.
考虑到意大利人口规模远小于中国，其能用于阻隔和救治的医疗资源、社会资源承载力堪忧。
Given that Italy's population is much smaller than China's, the medical and social resources that it can use to block and treat it are woefully inadequate.
欧洲已比中国多出一倍，而增势未明确减缓。
Europe is already twice as large as China, and the gains have not clearly slowed.
美国如期穿越了黄线，意味着总量超越中国已无悬念。
The U. S. crossed the yellow line on schedule, meaning there is no suspense of overtaking China.
若维持目前趋势，其与欧洲比肩甚至超越欧洲也已是大概率事件。
If the current trend is maintained, its parallelism with Europe and even its overtaking of Europe is already a high-probability event.
三、美国1/3确诊病例集中在纽约，二季度GDP或降50%图5美国确诊病例迅速突破3万。
One-third of confirmed cases in the United States are concentrated in New York, with GDP or 50% decline in the second quarter. Figure 5.
华盛顿州继纽约州之后成为美国第二个疫情“重大灾区”。
Washington, after New York State, became the second major disaster area in the United States.
截至22日，美国已有8个州宣布“居家隔离令”，覆盖美国人口的近三分之一。
By June 22, eight U.S. states had announced "home separation orders," covering nearly a third of the U.S. population.
纽约市长白思豪称，美国目前1/3的新冠肺炎确诊病例在纽约，这一情况短期内不会得到改善，“事实是，形势正在恶化”。
One-third of confirmed cases of pneumonia in the United States now occur in New York City, according to New York City's governor, a situation that won't improve in the short term.
特朗普总统已经启动《国防生产法案》，以“保证获得必要授权，优先生产政府合同项目，并将稀缺资源分配到最需要的地方”。
President Trump has launched the Defense Production Bill to "ensure the necessary authority to prioritize government-contracted projects and allocate scarce resources where they are most needed."
纽约证券交易所将于3月23日起首次关闭交易大厅，临时进行全面电子交易。
The New York Stock Exchange will close its trading halls for the first time on March 23 for full electronic trading on an ad hoc basis.
美国圣路易斯联邦储备银行行长詹姆斯·布拉德22日预测称，美国第二季度的失业率可能会达到30%，这意味着美国失业率将超过上世纪30年代“大萧条”时期。
The unemployment rate in the United States could reach 30 percent in the second quarter, meaning it will be higher than during the Great Depression of the 1930s, Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis President James Brad predicted Thursday.
他还预测美国第二季度GDP将出现50%的降幅。
He also predicted a 50% drop in U.S. GDP in the second quarter.
四、英国以“全面封锁“恐吓居民，默克尔被迫居家隔离图6英国首相约翰逊22日晚警告说，如果许多公众仍然不理会政府的劝告，保持社交距离以防止新冠病毒的传播，政府将会在24小时后宣布，效仿意大利、西班牙及法国，实施全面封闭措施，包括限制人员的流动并实施宵禁，以及关闭除食品店及药店之外的所有其它商店等。
British Prime Minister Gordon Johnson warned Thursday night that if many people continue to ignore government advice and keep their social distance to prevent the spread of the virus, the government will announce in 24 hours that it will follow Italy, Spain and France by imposing full closures, including restrictions on the movement of people and curfews, and closing all but food stores and pharmacies.
法国参议院与国民议会先后通过新冠肺炎疫情紧急应对法案。
The French Senate and then the National Assembly passed the New Crown Pneumonia Emergency Response Act.
法案规定，自法案生效之日起法国将设立为期2个月的公共卫生紧急状态。
The bill provides for the establishment of a public health emergency for a period of two months from the date of its entry into force.
在此期间，法国政府可通过发布行政法令的形式，限制人员外出和流动，征用必要的的物资与服务，并对企业和个人提供经济援助。
During this period, the French Government may, by means of administrative decrees, restrict the movement and movement of persons, requisition essential goods and services and provide economic assistance to enterprises and individuals.
西班牙宣布国家紧急状态再延长15天。
Spain extended the state of emergency for another 15 days.
西班牙男高音歌唱家普拉西多·多明戈证实感染新冠病毒。
Spanish tenor Prasido Domingo has confirmed a new crown virus.
希腊从当地时间23日早6点开始在全国范围实施全面封闭、全民禁足措施。
Greece from 23 local time from 6 a.m. to implement a comprehensive nationwide closure, the full ban measures.
根据俄政府令，23日起俄罗斯临时限制与所有国家的空中交通。
Russia imposed temporary restrictions on air traffic with all countries on May 23, according to a Russian government order.
除撤侨包机外，与每个国家仅保留一趟航线。
With the exception of the evacuation charter flights, with each country to retain only one route.
俄罗斯与中国间将保留莫斯科至北京往返航程。
Russia and China will retain Moscow to Beijing round trip.
图7意大利累计确诊接近6万例。
Figure 7 shows a cumulative total of nearly 60,000 diagnoses in Italy.
中国驻意大利大使介绍称，对中国支援意大利专家提出的改进意见，意大利几乎是照单全收、悉数采纳。
The Chinese ambassador to Italy said Italy had taken almost all the suggestions for improvement made by Chinese experts in support of Italy.
在意大利首都罗马，警方在街头截查行人并检查证件，如果发现有人在没有合理理由下出行的话，就会向其罚款。
In the Italian capital, Rome, police stop pedestrians in the streets and check documents and impose fines if people are found travelling without a reasonable excuse.
此外，除了超市、银行、药店及邮局外，所有商店都要关门停业。
In addition, all shops, except supermarkets, banks, pharmacies and post offices, are closed.
意大利政府向美国国防部长马克·埃斯珀呼吁，要求美国提供军事援助以抗击疫情，提供像口罩和呼吸机这样的关键医疗设备。
The Italian government has appealed to U.S. Defense Secretary Mark Espper to provide military aid to fight the outbreak and provide vital medical equipment such as masks and respirators.
同时，意大利政府还要求，驻扎在意大利的美国军事人员向意当局提供医疗人员和战地医院，以支持正在那里抗疫的意大利军队。
At the same time, the Italian Government has requested that United States military personnel stationed in Italy provide medical personnel and field hospitals to the Italian authorities in support of the Italian army, which is fighting the epidemic there.
图8德国总理默克尔当地时间22日晚宣布，在全国禁止2人以上的聚会，但家庭成员被排除在外。
German Chancellor Angela Merkel announced on the evening of the 22nd local time that more than two people are banned from gathering in the country, but family members are excluded.
专家称，如果不采取封锁措施，德国到4月底将有800万感染病例。
Experts say that without the blockade, Germany would have 8 million infections by the end of April.
德国各项民调也显示，超过2/3的民众赞成“封城”。
German polls also show that more than two-thirds of the population favours a "closed city."
默克尔本人将进行居家隔离，原因是曾为她提供过治疗的医生新冠病毒检测呈阳性。
Merkel herself will be quarantined because the doctor who treated her has tested positive for the new crown virus.
五、伊朗拒绝美国援助：“你们自己留着用吧！”图9美国总统特朗普22日称愿意帮助朝鲜、伊朗等国抗击疫情。
5. Iran Rejects US Aid: "Save it for yourselves!" Picture 9 US President Trump said on Tuesday that he would like to help countries such as North Korea and Iran to fight the epidemic.
但伊朗最高领袖哈梅内伊表示伊朗有能力独自应对各种层面的问题与挑战。
But Iran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei says Iran has the ability to deal with problems and challenges on its own.
哈梅内伊称，“美国自身都面临（物资）短缺。
"The US is facing a shortage [of goods] itself," he said.
所以你们还是留着自己用吧。
So keep it for your own use.
”美国在3月18日刚刚宣布对伊朗增加新的制裁措施。
The US just announced new sanctions against Iran on March 18.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】六、全球疫情数字速览：1、【高管降薪50%】美国联合航空公司3月收入预计将同比减少15亿美元。
According to statistics, the cut-off time for data before Feb. 28 is 17: 00 daily Beijing time. Starting Feb. 28, data by Caijing daily according to open data is 9: 00 a.m. Beijing time.
4月和5月还将削减50%的航班。
Flights will be cut by 50 per cent in April and May.
公司高级管理人员的工资也将削减50%。
The salaries of the company's top executives will also be cut by 50%.
2、【裁员2/3】澳大利亚第一大航空公司澳洲航空及旗下的捷星航空已停飞所有国际航班，于19日宣布三分之二的员工将从3月末开始暂时离开工作岗位，这意味着约二万人短期失业。
Australia's largest airline, Air Australia, and its Jetstar Airlines have suspended all international flights, announcing on the 19th that two-thirds of its workforce would be temporarily absent from work by the end of March, meaning about 20,000 people were unemployed for a short period.
新西兰航空公司也宣布削减85%的远程航线，并大幅裁员。
Air New Zealand also announced a cut of 85 per cent of its long-range routes and significant job cuts.
小结：国内多地周一重现早高峰，黄石成为湖北省首个全面解封的地级市。
Summary: China returned to early peak on Monday, Yellowstone Hubei Province as the first fully unsealed city.
国际奥组委确认正式考虑延期举办东京奥运会。
The International Olympic Committee has confirmed it is formally considering postponing the Games.
疫情令美国经济处在悬崖边缘，第二季度或出现50%衰退。
The epidemic has left the US economy on the brink of a 50% recession in the second quarter.
德国总理默克尔被迫居家隔离。
German Chancellor Angela Merkel was forced to stay in isolation.
意大利对中国专家组的建议照单全收。
Italy accepts the recommendations of the China Group of Experts.
